<p class="ql-align-justify">/在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归商家所有/</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>01</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>●开吃汕头老字号“豆花” ●</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201026/25b022506955400982b21e11d21f49c5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201026/fd9e52dcfb3544e5aca05844f3a663c5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201026/81ea4edd8a6d40de91c3669f66762eaf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201026/1954d96a57aa459fad47a70ef3a08d32.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>一舀就是完整的一块豆花</strong>，丝毫没有散开的架势，看得见的扎实感，几乎看不出水分，还没吃就能闻到一阵浓郁的豆香味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201026/a50315e8a93840d9984bf6dab44964b3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201026/a1290c26b3cd4d6b8b5a2d92e4e188e0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201026/a1290c26b3cd4d6b8b5a2d92e4e188e0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">利落的手法盛到瓷碗里后，<strong>再撒上芝麻、红糖、蔗糖三种材料制作而成的红糖霜</strong>，如富士山一般的豆花就出现在眼前。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201026/5f359222f54f4f5c98bfc21f1971e562.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">摇摇晃晃舀起一勺，<strong>豆花的质感丝滑又扎实</strong>，有了糖霜的加持，口感更加丰富。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201026/e145c0ec529a4fbd9fc2217228d30f66.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">轻轻一吸就滑进嘴里，<strong>浓浓的豆香味在口中散开</strong>，口感厚实绵密，每一口都清甜到心窝里，一碗下肚饱腹感十足！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>02</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>● 处处尽显温馨舒适 ●</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201026/1db01ac8009149d38d4512136d2fc18b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>舒适的桌椅，复古怀旧的装潢</strong>，与暖黄色的灯光相互映衬，墙上的壁画更是生动有趣，处处尽显温馨舒适。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201026/37270a42291e4bee986dbec6cc508b45.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还能闻到一股浓郁的豆香味，堂食就很舒服</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/在法律允许范围内，活动解释权归商家所有/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201026/94cb94355d074a35886bda9cc8d6ea24.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201026/19801eeffe2b4553b12e3cc5b5e6c004.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>#广场老牌豆花甜汤#</strong></p>
